2) Introducing the image tag IMG.
The <img> tag allows(elauz) us to add images to our web pages. 
(<img> etiketi, web sayfalarımıza resim eklememizi sağlar.)

	Features of <img> tag:
	  a) No closing tag.(No need for </img>)

	  b) No text being annotated(açıklamalı) by the <img> tag.
	 (<img> etiketi tarafından açıklama eklenmiş metin yok.)

	  c) Simly the <img> tag and some attributes(Öznitellikler).

	  d) The <img> tag has a src attribute.

	  e) src specifies where to get the image from.  
	      (Görüntünün nereden alınacağını belirtir.)

	  f) The source(src) is the URL for an image. 
    	  g) src attribute specifies where should get the image from and 
	     this is the URL for an image.

	  h) The <img> tag also have width and height attributes.
 	     They specify the size of the image in pixels. 
           i) The <img> tag has alt attribute. 
	      The alt attribute tells us about the image. 
 
Pixels are the unit of measurement(mejırmınt).
We will be using to size our images. 

